parameters:
Welcome, magical girl-sama... You are the first
magical girl-sama to visit us, but... (How on
earth...)

Is this place perhaps the demon's stronghold? It's
unbelievable that they've set up in such a
location.

Haa, is that so... Did you come here without
knowing anything?

I see. I'm not quite sure, but... Your boss is
here, right?

Is it Devil-sama you're referring to? Of course,
they are here...

Devil, you say? I have a feeling that everything
will be okay if we defeat that person.

(This is a dangerous magical girl... I have a
feeling that we need to inform all the demons and
deal with her on every floor...!)

Um, then please go through that staircase over
there. It's a bit intricate, but please enjoy the
Astalot Labyrinth...

You can go directly to Lord Devil's place from
that portal.

Welcome, magical girl-sama. You are the first
magical girl-sama to visit.

He's surprisingly polite for a demon. Why isn't he
attacking us?

Attack? This is the demon's stronghold, so if we
wanted to attack, we could do it anytime...
However, you have been referred to as a guest by
Lord Belzevia, so

I see... (He's surprisingly gentlemanly in his
response...)

Well then, magical girl-sama... What brings you
here today?
I hope to have a conversation with the devil
I came here to crush this place
I want to become a member of the demons
デヴィルとの対話を希望

Let me talk to your boss, Devil. We need to put an
end to this long battle.

Understood. Then, I will personally escort you
directly to Lord Devil's place through that
portal.
It's helpful that you get straight to the point.

Sorry, but I can't forgive all of you demons. I've
come here to crush every single one of you.

How terrifying you are. I understand... Well then,
I'll run away first.
Ah! Hey! What fast legs you have...

Alright, I guess there's no other choice. Let's
break through this labyrinth and head to Devil's
place.
デーモンの仲間になりたい

You might not believe it, but I actually wanted to
become your ally.

You might not believe it, but actually, I've been
wanting to become your ally.
To become our ally? Hmm... Please wait a moment...

Hmm! This is quite the wicked person...! You have
great potential... It would be good for you to
form a contract with Lord Devil. I will guide you.
Hehehe. I'm looking forward to it.
Hehehe. I'm looking forward to it.

Ahaha, it's impossible for someone like you who is
a good person. If you really want to become one,
you need to accumulate evil deeds and make enemies
out of humans and loli-monsters.

When we talk about evil deeds here, it's not
referring to karma, so be careful... Accumulating
small mischiefs won't cut it...

It seems you have returned. From now on, please
take care of us, Konoha-san. Well then, since you
have become one of us, we will need a new base.

When you take a break, you will be transported to
the Demon Garden. If you are defeated by enemies,
you will also be portaled there.

Just because you have become one of us demons, it
doesn't mean that the wandering demons won't
attack you anymore, so please be careful.

Whenever you have the chance, make sure to absorb
the power of your comrades. That's what being a
demon is all about, so please never forget that...
